rows.label: tlk42400045_02_msg0001
rows.name:
My employer, Lapacoll-san, tried to flee
in the night, but he was caught by the
Invidian army... mo.

rows.label: tlk42400045_02_msg0002
rows.name:
I never dreamed he was making a dangerous poison
called Thanatitan, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400045_02_msg0003
rows.name:
I thought he was making the new Pollen Orb product
I came up with, the Mushroomy Pollen Orb... mo.

rows.label: tlk42400045_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Anyway, my employer was caught and now
Tolulu is unemployed, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400045_02_msg0005
rows.name:
Is there anyone looking for a
helper, mo?
